data.title: The biggest and fastest supplier of Karaoke files
data.text:
Welcome to our new site

This new site features better browsing and viewing by title and/or artist is easier and clearer. You can select the format and label you want as a 2nd step and simplify the choices by filtering out formats you don’t want.

You can register an existing account here with your existing username and password if you have one. (We will add your entire previous purchase history within a few days so you can easily download ANY and ALL older orders WHENEVER you choose to.)

Partially discounted price held until 2024

Though the first song will CONTINUE to be charged at £1.66** (normal price) on all orders due to the high charge by third party payment processing companies on small orders

** disc orders will be subject to a charge of £6 (which includes shipping)

* all prices subject to VAT where applicable
